body: ## Expected Behavior Example works without issue. ## Actual Behavior Accessing localhost:8088 works fine, but shows a little box "DNS resolution failed" in the lower right corner as soon as I'm trying to insert text in the textbox. Commandline shows this error: ## Steps to Reproduce the Problem 1. Clone the https://github.com/temporalio/docker-compose.git 2. docker-compose up 3. open localhost:8088 ## Specifications - Version: temporalio/auto-setup:1.13.0, temporalio/web:1.12.0, temporalio/admin-tools:1.13.0 - Platform: Mac (M1)

comments.body: Verified that this is no longer repro on v1.24 at least.

title: DNS resolution failed on temporalio/docker-compose example
